Package se.lypson.common

Interface Summary
IComparator An interface for comparing objects.
IFilter An interface for filters with interchangeable filter criteria.
IStringTransformer An interface for classes transforming objects into string.
ITextChangedObserver An interface for classes observing text changed events.
 

Class Summary
MultiTapKeypad A class for interpreting input of the keys 0-9, * and #, the typical keys availableon a mobile phone, as character input.
Settings The Settings class stores values for keys, much like a hash table.
StandardComparators A class containing comparators for standard types.
Utilities The Utilities class contains static methods that can be useful but does not require a class of their own.
 

Exception Summary
NoSuchKeyException Thrown to indicate an operation could not be completed because a required key was missing.
